---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms | Linda Della Industries" description="Website and inquiry terms for Linda Della Industries.">
  <SiteHeader />
  <main id="main-content" class="legal-page section-shell">
    <article class="shell legal-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow"><span>Terms</span> Effective July 16, 2026</p>
      <h1>Website terms.</h1>
      <p class="legal-lede">This site describes services offered by William Doran IV under the Linda Della Industries name. Sending an inquiry does not create a client relationship, reserve a project, or guarantee acceptance.</p>
      <h2>Engagements</h2><p>Any project begins only after both parties agree in writing to scope, responsibilities, price, third-party costs, data handling, acceptance criteria, and payment terms. The founding-client offer is subject to fit and availability. Any seven-day delivery period begins on the kickoff date stated in the written agreement, after required payment, access, sample data, and client contacts have been provided.</p>
      <h2>No professional advice</h2><p>Website content is general information, not legal, medical, financial, employment, privacy, security, or regulatory advice. Regulated or high-stakes work may require qualified specialists and may be declined.</p>
      <h2>AI limitations</h2><p>AI systems can be inaccurate, inconsistent, or fail unexpectedly. Proposed workflows should use proportionate testing, monitoring, access controls, and human review. No business outcome, revenue result, or uninterrupted operation is guaranteed.</p>
      <h2>Third-party services</h2><p>Projects and this website may rely on third-party hosting, form, API, or software providers governed by their own terms. Third-party usage costs are not included unless a written project agreement says otherwise.</p>
      <h2>Site content</h2><p>Nothing on this site grants permission to copy or present Linda Della Industries branding or original site content as another business’s work. Third-party names, trademarks, and linked materials remain subject to their respective owners’ rights and terms.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2><p>Questions may be sent to <a href="mailto:willdoraniv@gmail.com">willdoraniv@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </article>
  </main>
  <SiteFooter />
</BaseLayout>
